item.dc:creator: @snowycards snowycards
item.description:
@snowycards wrote:

Coldbloodio:

If your gonna delete stuff you need to read what the error says on your compiler…Normally when you delete something, There is another block of code in your server that supports the code you deleted…If you deleted the code it supports…What does it support now? An error…Read the compile errors and go to the line and read what the code says and delete parts of it that you think are supporting the summoning. If you want to add or edit the songs in the music list just find what the text says and search for it in client.java. You should find some stuff which you can edit and have it what you want to say.
